    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Engines</a> * Pulsar</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Chandra-crab.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c9/Chandra-crab.jpg/330px-Chandra-crab.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c9/Chandra-crab.jpg/500px-Chandra-crab.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c9/Chandra-crab.jpg/960px-Chandra-crab.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Chandra-crab.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Crab_Nebula\">Crab Nebula</a> with <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Crab_Pulsar\">Crab pulsar</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Pulsar</b>,<br />\na <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> compatible chess engine by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Adams&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mike Adams (page does not exist)\">Mike Adams</a>, written in <a href=\"/C\" title=\"C\">C</a>. \nThe development started in October 1998, and with help from people on <a href=\"/index.php?title=Internet_Chess_Club&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Internet Chess Club (page does not exist)\">ICC's</a> channel 64, most notably <a href=\"/Peter_McKenzie\" title=\"Peter McKenzie\">Kiwipete</a> and <a href=\"/Vincent_Diepeveen\" title=\"Vincent Diepeveen\">Diepeveen</a>, Pulsar started its life in December and January of 1998/99 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \nIn June 2003 Pulsar has been released for the first time. In the meantime, Pulsar is available for <a href=\"/X86\" title=\"X86\">x86</a> and <a href=\"/X86-64\" title=\"X86-64\">x86-64</a> under <a href=\"/Windows\" title=\"Windows\">Windows</a>, <a href=\"/Linux\" title=\"Linux\">Linux</a> or <a href=\"/Mac_OS\" title=\"Mac OS\">Mac OS</a>, as well as for <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mobile_phone\">Mobiles</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tablet_computer\">Tablets</a> under <a href=\"/index.php?title=IOS&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"IOS (page does not exist)\">iOS</a> and <a href=\"/Android\" title=\"Android\">Android</a>. \nPulsar plays orthodox chess, as well as various chess variants. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Variants\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Variants</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#Chess_Engine\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Engine</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#Misc\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Variants\">Selected Variants</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pulsar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Variants\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Atomic_Chess\" title=\"Atomic Chess\">Atomic Chess</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Chess960\" title=\"Chess960\">Chess960</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Crazyhouse\" title=\"Crazyhouse\">Crazyhouse</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Losing_Chess\" title=\"Losing Chess\">Losing Chess</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Shatranj\" title=\"Shatranj\">Shatranj</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pulsar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Pulse\" title=\"Pulse\">Pulse</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Search_Instability\" title=\"Search Instability\">Search Instability</a> </li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pulsar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pulsar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=134326\">For Mike Adams: Some querstions about Pulsar</a> by <a href=\"/Arturo_Ochoa\" title=\"Arturo Ochoa\">Arturo Ochoa</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 21, 2000</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=129985\">is this nullmove? problems in pulsar algorithm</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Adams&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mike Adams (page does not exist)\">Mike Adams</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 20, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=39335\">release of pulsar</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Adams&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mike Adams (page does not exist)\">Mike Adams</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, October 01, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=32485\">Command to autoload engines fcp scp for set game match?</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Adams&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mike Adams (page does not exist)\">Mike Adams</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, October 05, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=43149\">pulsarV2.01d release</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Adams&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mike Adams (page does not exist)\">Mike Adams</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, June 26, 2003</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=43201\">pulsarV2.01f release</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Adams&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mike Adams (page does not exist)\">Mike Adams</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, June 30, 2003</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=43261\">new look for pulsar page</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Adams&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mike Adams (page does not exist)\">Mike Adams</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, July 05, 2003</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pulsar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=14075\">hashing, check extensions and depth</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Adams&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mike Adams (page does not exist)\">Mike Adams</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 27, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Check_Extensions\" title=\"Check Extensions\">Check Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=6976\">Questions on issues surrounding releasing code</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Adams&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mike Adams (page does not exist)\">PulsarMike</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, November 28, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=28370\">question about releasing pulsar under gpl</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Adams&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mike Adams (page does not exist)\">Mike Adams</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 12, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=28436\">alpha beta hashing and move ordering</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Adams&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mike Adams (page does not exist)\">Mike Adams</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 15, 2009</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pulsar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=45978\">Pulsar page has moved</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Adams&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mike Adams (page does not exist)\">Mike Adams</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 13, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51931\">PulsarChess for iOS</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Adams&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mike Adams (page does not exist)\">Mike Adams</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 10, 2014</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pulsar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63333\">Mac binary of pulsar2009-b chess variants program released</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Adams&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mike Adams (page does not exist)\">Mike Adams</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 04, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63336\">Linux binary of pulsar2009-b chess variants program released</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Adams&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mike Adams (page does not exist)\">Mike Adams</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 04, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=69955\">understanding android chess engine binary formats</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Adams&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mike Adams (page does not exist)\">Mike Adams</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 19, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=70461\">Mike Adams - introducing myself as a Chess Programmer</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Adams&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mike Adams (page does not exist)\">Mike Adams</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 10, 2019</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pulsar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Engine\">Chess Engine</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pulsar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Engine\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.lanternchess.com/pulsar/\">Pulsar Chess engine</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/pulsar-chess-variants/id839640447?mt=8\">Pulsar - Chess Variants on the App Store</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.lantern.michaeladams.pulsarchessengine&amp;hl=en\">Pulsar Chess Engine - Apps on Google Play</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.computerchess.org.uk/ccrl/404/cgi/engine_details.cgi?print=Details&amp;each_game=1&amp;eng=Pulsar%202009-9b\">Pulsar 2009-9b</a> in <a href=\"/CCRL\" title=\"CCRL\">CCRL 40/4</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pulsar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pulsar\">Pulsar from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pulsar_(disambiguation)\">Pulsar (disambiguation) from Wikipedia</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IBM_RS64#RS64-III\">Pulsar (IBM RS64-III) from Wikipedia</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pulsar_(comics)\">Pulsar (comics) from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pulsar_(band)\">Pulsar</a> - <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Strands_of_the_Future\">The Strands of the Future</a> (1976), <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/KpL5htneI-c?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pulsar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">A <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Compositing\">composite</a> image of the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Crab_Nebula\">Crab Nebula</a> showing the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/X-ray_astronomy\">X-ray</a> (blue), and optical (red) images <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Superimposition\">superimposed</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikimedia_Commons\">Wikimedia Commons</a>, Image from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://hubblesite.org/image/1248/news_release/2002-24\">HubbleSite: Image - Combined X-Ray and Optical Images of the Crab Nebula</a>, September 19, 2002, Just when it seemed like the summer movie season had ended, two of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/NASA\">NASA's</a> Great Observatories have produced their own action movie. Multiple observations made over several months with NASA's <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chandra_X-ray_Observatory\">Chandra X-ray Observatory</a> and the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hubble_Space_Telescope\">Hubble Space Telescope</a> captured the spectacle of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matter\">matter</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Antimatter\">antimatter</a> propelled to near the speed of light by the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Crab_Pulsar\">Crab pulsar</a>, a rapidly rotating <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neutron_star\">neutron star</a> the size of Manhattan ...</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.lanternchess.com/pulsar/\">Pulsar Chess engine - Some History</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301011549\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic cont